Raspberry Pi library for GPIO, 1-Wire, SPI, System Time Counter (STC) access. As
an example of usage there has been provided API for handling various popular
sensors like Dallas DS family of temperature sensors (e.g. ds18b20), HC-SR04
distance sensor, PISO shift register.

Expect more detailed documentation and sensors support in the future. For now
look for examples in /examples directory.

